<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
<p>Hamza Boutou built the Tasks To Do app as a free app. This SERVICE is provided by Hamza Boutou at no cost and is intended for use as is.</p>
<p>This page is used to inform users about our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information if anyone decides to use our Service.</p>
<p>Since we do not collect any personal data, we do not use or share any personal information.</p>
<p>The terms used in this Privacy Policy have the same meanings as in our Terms and Conditions, which is accessible in the app, unless otherwise defined in this Privacy Policy.</p>

<p><strong>Information Collection and Use</strong></p>
<p>For a better experience while using our Service, please note that we do not collect any personally identifiable information from users.</p>
<p>As we do not collect any data, we do not use any third-party services that collect personal data.</p>

<p><strong>Log Data</strong></p>
<p>We do not collect any Log Data. Since we do not have data collection mechanisms in place, no information such as your device’s Internet Protocol (“IP”) address, device name, or operating system version is collected by us.</p>

<p><strong>Cookies</strong></p>
<p>This Service does not use cookies or any similar tracking technologies. Since we do not collect data, we do not use cookies to collect or store any personal information.</p>

<p><strong>Service Providers</strong></p>
<p>Since we do not collect any personal data, we do not employ any third-party companies or individuals for data-related tasks. Therefore, we have no third-party services to disclose.</p>

<p><strong>Security</strong></p>
<p>As we do not collect or store any personal information, we do not have specific security measures related to personal data. However, we strive to ensure that the app operates securely and efficiently.</p>

<p><strong>Links to Other Sites</strong></p>
<p>This Service may contain links to other sites. If you click on a third-party link, you will be directed to that site. Please note that these external sites are not operated by us. Therefore, we strongly advise you to review the Privacy Policy of these websites. We have no control over, and assume no responsibility for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party sites or services.</p>

<p><strong>Children’s Privacy</strong></p>
<p>This Service is intended for use by individuals of all ages. We do not specifically target or collect personal identifiable information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and you are aware that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us so that we can take necessary actions to address the situation.</p>

<p><strong>Changes to This Privacy Policy</strong></p>
<p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Therefore, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. These changes are effective immediately after they are posted on this page.</p>

<p><strong>Contact Us</strong></p>
<p>If you have any questions or suggestions about this Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at boutou.hb@gmail.com.</p>

